channel.title: Delta Pking Problem
channel.description: My source is Paradise Planet and I fixed everything else but I can't seem to fix this issue. When you are Pking and you kill somebody, they fall but they don't die and you just kill them over and over again. After about 5 or so minutes they finally die and it says "This player is not in the wilderness!" So I was wondering if anyone knew how to fix this
